	--------------------------------------------
	## iostat (io stat)
	---------
	Whatâ€™s happening? Prints CPU and I/O statistics
	Usage : To review CPU usage , and I/O load for all devices including SWAP partion

	(!) To see which device is used as swap space , use 
	->swapon -s
	->cat /proc/swap

	------------------------------------------------
	IOSTAT EXAMPLES
	------------------------------------------------

	------------------------------------
	# 1 Show cpu usage
	------------------------------------
	iostat -c

	avg-cpu:  %user   %nice %system %iowait  %steal   %idle
    5.68      0.00    0.52    2.03    0.00   91.76

	------------------------------------
	# 2 Show network usage
	------------------------------------
	iostat -n

	